Dan: I don't remember.

00:10:43.150 --> 00:10:46.760
Dan: Oh, not much.

00:10:46.760 --> 00:10:47.940
Just went to see my family yesterday.

00:10:47.940 --> 00:10:48.960
What about you?

00:10:48.960 --> 00:10:51.070
Vanessa: Aww, what a cute dog.

00:10:51.070 --> 00:10:52.830
Dan: Yeah, he's a sweetie.

00:10:52.830 --> 00:10:54.900
Vanessa: Have you been in Asheville for a
while?

