00:11:06.840 --> 00:11:11.150
Vanessa: I have a unicorn dog, not I want
a corn dog.

00:11:11.150 --> 00:11:15.910
Dan: I thought you said, "I want a corn dog."

00:11:15.910 --> 00:11:16.910
Unicorn dog.

00:11:16.910 --> 00:11:19.440
Vanessa: Aww, What a cute ... What a cutie.

00:11:19.440 --> 00:11:21.470
But, I said, "Cutie dog".

00:11:21.470 --> 00:11:23.920
Vanessa: Aww, what a cute dog.

00:11:23.920 --> 00:11:24.920
Dan: Mmm.

00:11:24.920 --> 00:11:25.920
Thanks.

